N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1290.12 - Obstruction of expansion or contraction joints prohibited

State Regulations

No person shall place any furniture, machine or equipment
over any expansion or contraction joint unless one end of such furniture, machine or equipment is free to permit expansion or
contraction. Notes
